《'''小舍得'''》（{{lang-en|''A Love for Dilemma''}}）是中国大陆一部家庭教育题材電視劇，該劇編劇為[[周艺飞|周艺飞]]，導演為[[张晓波|张晓波]]，总制片人為徐晓鸥，[[宋佳|宋佳]]、[[佟大为|佟大为]]、[[蒋欣|蒋欣]]、[[李佳航|李佳航]]、[[张国立|张国立]]等人主演。2021年4月11日起在[[東方衛視|東方衛視]]、[[央视八套|央视八套]]和[[爱奇艺|爱奇艺]]等平台播出<ref>{{cite news |title=《小舍得》周日开播 |url=https://hznews.hangzhou.com.cn/wenti/content/2021-04/07/content_7942038.html |publisher=杭州網 |date=2021-04-07|accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411003351/https://hznews.hangzhou.com.cn/wenti/content/2021-04/07/content_7942038.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該劇以南俪、田雨岚兩個家庭的三代人親子關係和家庭子女教育為線索來展開<ref>{{cite news |title=小舍得 |url=https://www.iqiyi.com/lib/m_9000000001016914.html |publisher=愛奇藝 |accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516155850/http://www.iqiyi.com/lib/m_9000000001016914.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=《小舍得》聚焦“小升初”在有爱的环境享受童年 |url=https://m.sohu.com/a/459455513_162758/?pvid=000115_3w_a |publisher=光明網  |date=2021-04-07|accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411031047/https://m.sohu.com/a/459455513_162758/?pvid=000115_3w_a |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=聚焦“小升初”，《小舍得》探讨家长为啥会焦虑 |url=https://m.sohu.com/a/459351180_260616/?pvid=000115_3w_a |publisher=澎湃新聞 |date=2021-04-07|accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411031052/https://m.sohu.com/a/459351180_260616/?pvid=000115_3w_a |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=《小欢喜》姊妹篇《小舍得》将播 宋佳蒋欣玩命“拼娃” |url=https://news.syd.com.cn/system/2021/04/07/011910047.shtml |publisher=瀋陽網 |date=2021-04-07|accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411003352/https://news.syd.com.cn/system/2021/04/07/011910047.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=电视剧《小舍得》11日开播 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/459517607_571524 |publisher=搜狐 |date=2021-04-08|accessdate=2021-04-11 |archive-date=202